      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Software &amp; AI engineering firm</p>
        <h1 class="reveal">We build AI software for institutions that can't afford for it to <em>break</em>.</h1>
        <p class="lede reveal">Codxperts is trusted by <strong>courts, government regulators, and law firms</strong>, and is the team that built DigiLawyer, Pakistan's first AI legal platform. We design, build, and ship applied-AI software for clients worldwide.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions reveal">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a project <span class="arr" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
          <a href="#work" class="btn btn-ghost">See the work</a>
